{
  "id": "L25",
  "title": "A Casual Birthday Party",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Welcome to a French birthday party, or 'une fête d'anniversaire' ! We'll learn how to congratulate the host and chat with other guests."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V01",
      "data": {
        "Une fête d'anniversaire": "A birthday party"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Joyeux anniversaire",
        "meaning": "Happy birthday"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L25_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "Joyeux",
        "phonetic": "[ʒwa.jø]",
        "tip": "The 'oy' sounds like 'wa' in 'water'. The 'x' at the end is silent."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V02",
      "data": {
        "Un cadeau": "A gift"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "C'est pour toi",
        "meaning": "This is for you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V03",
      "data": {
        "Un verre": "A glass"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "S'il te plaît",
        "meaning": "Please (informal)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L25_S01",
      "title": "Arriving at the Party",
      "setting": "You've arrived at your classmate Camille's party. You find her and then go to get a drink where another guest, Léo, is standing.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Congratulate the host",
          "chatbot_message": "Salut ! Merci d'être là !"
        },
        {
          "title": "Give your gift",
          "chatbot_message": "Merci beaucoup ! C'est super gentil !"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for a glass",
          "chatbot_message": "Oh, merci ! Prends quelque chose à boire. (You go to the drinks table and see another guest) Salut !"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great! Now that you have a drink, it's time to mingle. Let's learn how to start a conversation with someone new."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je m'appelle...",
        "meaning": "My name is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Comment tu connais Camille ?",
        "meaning": "How do you know Camille?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L25_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "Connais",
        "phonetic": "[kɔ.nɛ]",
        "tip": "Like many French verbs, the 's' at the end of 'connais' is silent."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V04",
      "data": {
        "Le cours": "The class"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V05",
      "data": {
        "Une amie": "A friend (female)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Nous sommes dans le même cours",
        "meaning": "We are in the same class"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Et toi ?",
        "meaning": "And you?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L25_S02",
      "title": "Joining a Conversation",
      "setting": "You see a guest named Sophie standing by herself and you decide to introduce yourself.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Introduce yourself",
          "chatbot_message": "Salut ! Je suis Sophie.",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_name": "Extract the user's name from their message"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask how she knows Camille",
          "chatbot_message": "Enchantée, {user_name} !"
        },
        {
          "title": "Explain how you know Camille",
          "chatbot_message": "Je suis une amie de Camille. Et toi ?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Knowing how to politely leave a conversation is just as important as starting one. Let's learn a few phrases to help you exit gracefully."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "C'était sympa",
        "meaning": "It was nice"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "À plus tard",
        "meaning": "See you later"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L25_V06",
      "data": {
        "L'invitation": "The invitation"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Merci pour l'invitation",
        "meaning": "Thank you for the invitation"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "La fête est super",
        "meaning": "The party is great"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L25_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Au revoir",
        "meaning": "Goodbye"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L25_S03",
      "title": "Leaving the Party",
      "setting": "It's time to go home. You need to politely end your chat with Sophie and then find Camille to thank her and say goodbye.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Politely end the conversation",
          "chatbot_message": "...et voilà, c'est mon film préféré."
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the host for the invitation",
          "chatbot_message": "À plus ! (You find Camille) {user_name} ! Tu pars déjà ?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say the party was great and say goodbye",
          "chatbot_message": "De rien ! Je suis contente que tu sois venu."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}